:

1. *Zatvor* je sprovela policija (The police carried out the arrest). 
2. U *zatvoru* je proveo tri godine (He spent three years in prison).
3. On je bio u *zatvoru* zbog prekršaja (He was in prison for violations).
4. *Zatvor* je bila najteža mjera (Imprisonment was the harshest measure). 
5. Njihov *zatvor* je oslobođen (Their prison was released).